        "title": "feat(feishu): configure card footer",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nFeishu agent replies already render structured cards with a gray note footer, but operators cannot customize that footer from config. This makes the main agent card footer fixed to the generated `Agent / Model / Provider` metadata instead of allowing a deployment-specific label or operational note.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nThis adds a Feishu plugin `cardFooter` config field and wires it into the existing structured-card note rendering path instead of adding a new card layout. The setting is shared config, so it works at `channels.feishu.cardFooter` and can be overridden per account with `channels.feishu.accounts.<id>.cardFooter`.\n\nWhen unset or blank, Feishu cards keep the current generated footer. That preserves existing behavior while giving operators a small, explicit customization hook for main agent cards and other agent reply cards.\n\n## User Impact\n\nUsers can configure a custom footer note for Feishu/Lark agent cards. The value is used on both streaming cards and complete structured-card replies. Existing configs continue to show the current generated `Agent: ... | Model: ... | Provider: ...` footer when `cardFooter` is not set.\n\n## Evidence\n\nLive Feishu/Lark behavior proof on PR head `1ebecc1156ea56026f507274dbf894d45bf93864`:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"pr\": 95479,\n  \"head\": \"1ebecc1156ea56026f507274dbf894d45bf93864\",\n  \"target\": \"user:o…e7cf\",\n  \"accountId\": \"default\",\n  \"staticCompleteCard\": {\n    \"footer\": \"OpenClaw PR95479 footer proof 20260621043626\",\n    \"sent\": true,\n    \"messageId\": \"om_x10…39fc\",\n    \"readbackContentType\": \"interactive\",\n    \"readbackContainsFooter\": true,\n    \"readbackExcerpt\": \"Static complete card footer proof for PR95479. stamp=20260621043626\\n<font color='grey'>OpenClaw PR95479 footer proof 20260621043626</font>\"\n  },\n  \"streamingCard\": {\n    \"footer\": \"OpenClaw PR95479 streaming footer proof 20260621044718\",\n    \"cardId\": \"765370…0586\",\n    \"messageId\": \"om_x10…5448\",\n    \"closedVisible\": true,\n    \"logs\": [\n      \"Started streaming: cardId=<redacted>, messageId=<redacted>\",\n      \"Closed streaming: cardId=<redacted>\"\n    ],\n    \"messageGet\": {\n      \"contentType\": \"interactive\",\n      \"containsFooter\": true,\n      \"excerpt\": \"Streaming card footer content proof for PR95479. stamp=20260621044718\\nfinalized\\n<font color='grey'>OpenClaw PR95479 streaming footer proof 20260621044718</font>\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\nLocal verification:\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run extensions/feishu/src/reply-dispatcher.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/config-schema.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/accounts.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-tsgo.mjs -p test/tsconfig/tsconfig.extensions.test.json --incremental --tsBuildInfoFile .artifacts/tsgo-cache/extensions-test.tsbuildinfo`\n- `node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check extensions/feishu/src/config-schema.ts extensions/feishu/src/reply-dispatcher.ts extensions/feishu/src/config-schema.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/reply-dispatcher.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/accounts.test.ts extensions/feishu/openclaw.plugin.json docs/channels/feishu.md`\n- `git diff --check`\n\n## Related Issues\n\n- Partially overlaps https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/60748\n- Partially overlaps https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/93667\n- Partially overlaps https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/issues/59360",
